English:
@d0@q0Typed on the worker's data pad is the following warning:
<i><color=#ffffff>They're in the vents! In the ceiling! Do not use your jetpack and get too close to them or they will come out of the vents!</color></i>
<i><color=#ffffff>They are never-ending! I killed hundreds and they just kept coming!</color></i>
<i><color=#ffffff>They only stopped when I landed back on the floor.</color></i>
@p9 @d0@q0<color=#ffffff><i>The place is filled with egg sacs and alien nests! </i></color><color=#ffffff><i>He's taken over the main control room. For some reason, those who tried to fight just outside of the room where he was were just overrun with those creatures!</i></color>
<color=#ffffff><i>Heed my advice, and if you choose to face him, stay in the room you fight him in! If you must leave, travel back to the upper hangar! Don't stay just outside his room!</i></color>
@p9 @d0@q0<color=#ffffff>-</color><color=#ffff00>Be careful using your jetpack. It can keep you out of range of melee enemies but may attract the attention of ranged spiders from the vents. It might be safer to leave your jetpack off.</color>
<color=#ffffff>-</color><color=#ffff00>When facing whomever is in the control room, stay inside the room they are in. If you must retreat, do so all the way back to the upper hangar.</color>
<color=#ffffff>-</color><color=#ffff00>If you see alien eggs or nests, destroy them before they can spawn additional creatures.</color>
<color=#ffffff>-</color><color=#ffff00>The schematics of the station show several repair stations. Make use of them to keep your armor repaired as armor loses protection based on it's durability level and double check you're using the right boosts!</color>

Chinese (simplified):
@d0 @q0 工作人员的数据板上写着以下警告:
<i><color=#ffffff>他们在通风管里！就在天花板上！不要用喷气背包靠的太近，否则它们会从通风口出来！</color></i>
<i><color=#ffffff>他们无穷无尽！我杀了几百只，但是还是继续出现！</color></i>
<i><color=#ffffff>只有当我回到地板上时他们才不会涌出来.</color></i>
@p9 @d0 @q0 <color=#ffffff><i>这个地方到处都是卵囊和外星生物的巢穴 </i></color><color=#ffffff><i>他接管了主控制室。不知道为什么，所有想要还击的人一到他所在的房间边上就会被那些生物淹没</i></color>
<color=#ffffff><i>听我的建，如果你选择面对他，就留在你与他战斗的房间里！如果你不得不离开，返回上层机库！不要在他的房间外面待着！</i></color>
@p9 @d0 @q0 <color=#ffffff>-</color><color=#ffff00>谨慎使用你的喷气背包。它确实可以让你远离近战敌人的攻击，但可能会引起来自通风口的远程蜘蛛的注意。关掉喷气背包可能反而更安全.</color>
<color=#ffffff>-</color><color=#ffff00>无论你怎么对付房间里的那个东西，一定要保证留在他的房间内。如果有必要撤退，一直撤退到上层机库.</color>
<color=#ffffff>-</color><color=#ffff00>如果您看到外星生物卵或巢穴，请在它们产生更多怪物之前将其摧毁.</color>
<color=#ffffff>-</color><color=#ffff00>空间站的设计图图上标注了几个维修站。利用它们来修复你的护甲，因为盔甲会根据其耐久度降低防护能力，并且确保你是否使用了正确的增强器!</color>

English:
@d0<color=#ff0000>Your orders are simple. Take over that communications station and change the market price data for {Eden_String}. Make it look like the price is skyrocketing. Then we can come in and sell our own {Eden_String} for a huge profit.</color>
@p9 @d0<color=#ff0000>Not to mention with everyone looking to buy them to get in on the market we'll make a killing raiding all those freighters!</color>
<color=#ff0000>Of course, spreading rumors about certain Traders Guild executives couldn't hurt either. Oh and do try not to kill anyone, you can use the hostages in case someone shows up to stop you.</color>
<color=#ff0000>- Korvax</color>

Chinese (simplified):
@d0 <color=#ff0000>你的命令很简单. 接管该通信站并更改{Eden_String}的市场价格数据.让它看起来像价格暴涨. 然后我们可以进入并出售我们自己的{Eden_String}获得巨额利润.</color>
@p9 @d0 <color=#ff0000>更不用说每个人都想进入市场来买这东西，我们就可以通过袭击他们的货船来大赚一笔!</color>
<color=#ff0000>当然，散布关于某些贸易商会高管的谣言也不会有什么坏处。哦，不要杀任何人，有人出现阻止你的时候你可以用人质威胁他们.</color>
<color=#ff0000>- Korvax</color>

English:
You can only obtain deuterium from dense or rich ice asteroids found in special asteroid fields. You can find them all over the place but only around cold stars like class M or class D.
@p9You can only mine these asteroids with special ice mining lasers. They come in two varieties, a manual version and an automatic version.

The ice takes up a lot of space and I recommend having on-board deconstructors to break down the ice for you.

@p9Be wary of bandit attacks as they see miners as helpless targets. Bring some miniguns or flak to keep them at bay.

You can find better ice in the galactic region of Solitude, but it is a longer trip to sell your ice.

Good luck out there!

Chinese (simplified):
你只能从在特殊小行星区发现的致密或丰富的冰小行星中获得氘.你可以在任何地方找到它们，但只有在像M级或d级这样的冷恒星周围才会出现
@p9 你只能用特殊的冰采矿激光来开采这些小行星.它们有两种型号，手动版和自动版.冰矿一般要占据很大的空间，我建议使用船上的解构器来为你分解冰.

@p9 小型海盗的袭击，因为他们把矿工视为无防护的目标.带些小型火炮或高射炮来牵制他们.你可以在银河的外围地区找到更好的冰，但要卖掉你的冰你需要飞的更远.祝你好运!

English:
@q0You have to help us! Our ship was struck by an interdiction mine that pulled us out of warp!
If there was an interdiction mine out here you can bet someone put it there for a reason.
@p9 @q0We are carrying a valuable member of the Traders Guild executive board. We cannot allow bandits to capture or kill him!
Please, will you help defend our ship until we can get our warp drive back online?
Our generators must remain online. If our ship loses power then it's all over. Our escorts will help out as much as they can.
@p9 @q0<color=#ffff00>WARNING: Once accepted, the mission will start automatically and cannot be reset or completed again from this sector.</color>
<color=#ffff00>Only one person can accept this mission.</color>
<color=#ffff00>You must remain near the VIP Transport for the duration of the mission or it will fail.
Only start the mission when you are ready.</color>

