@p9 @d0<color=#00ff00>The interface portal will remain open for 2 minutes upon activation, and then stay closed for 5 minutes. Make sure all participants are ready and well equipped before entering the simulation.</color>
<color=#00ff00>Make sure all participants are wearing their preferred armor with full durability before entering the simulation.</color>
@p9 @d0<color=#00ff00>Before entering the simulation, all participants should make sure the mission </color><color=#ff00ff>The Dead Chapter 2</color><color=#00ff00> is currently active in their PDA. You will have 60 minutes to successfully complete the simulation before you must start over. </color>
<color=#00ff00>Don't wander too far off course, there is nothing else to find. The map displays all relevant points of interest.</color>
<color=#00ff00>This is the last cry of Refuge. Remember us.</color>

